ugins.</strong></p>\n<p>Downloadable at: <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/rss-just-better/" target="_blank">https://wordpress.org/plugins/rss-just-better/</a></p>\n<p><strong>Nothing fancy:  I have just linked it to my new domain name. I guess my own name was too difficult to remember to most of my readers.</strong></p>\n<p>I see also many unanswered (and unapproved) comments in the comments section of my blog and in the plugins pages of wordpress.org. I&#8217;ll do my best to answer them in the following days (if the posters are still around).</p>\n<p>Should you see errors or broken links, please shout it out via the contact form or in the comments. I still need to tweak a bit the new website.</p>\n<p>Cheers</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~4/TlV9V_2w1FQ" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-updated-to-version-1-4/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:63:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-updated-to-version-1-4/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:39:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"New webhosting";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s: