";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:80:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-wp-plugin-version-1-3-released/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sat, 23 Feb 2013 20:03:48 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"http://stefonthenet.com/?p=1346";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:362:"Here we go again. Previous version was 1.1. Version 1.2 has never been released. Long due release. Changes are as follows: New Feature: It&#8217;s possible to disable the reverse chronological order established by default. Normally, this results in a chronological order but not always. I.e. Google news will not be in chronological order. New Feature: [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Stef";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1175:"<p>Here we go again. Previous version was 1.1. Version 1.2 has never been released.</p>\n<p>Long due release. Changes are as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li> New Feature: It&#8217;s possible to disable the reverse chronological order established by default. Normally, this results in a chronological order but not always. I.e. Google news will not be in chronological order.\n<li> New Feature: Added &#8220;Serbia&#8221; to the list of Google News countries\n<li> New Feature: Added &#8220;More Top News&#8221; to the list of Google News topics\n<li> Change: Added more comments to code\n<li> Change: Google News attributes for shortcode are now the same as for widget variables (to avoid confusion)\n<li> Bug Fix: Non-latin alphabeths and non-standard chars (Google news locations) are now displayed properly\n<li> Bug Fix: Image URL for rss icon in shortcode is now correct\n<li> Bug Fix: Standard Google News feed URL has been changed (by Google)\n<li> Bug Fix: Location as null string does not deafult to usa (??) (Google news)\n<li> Bug Fix: urlencoding text for Google News searches\n</ul>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~4/0JpMa-qCFhM" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-wp-plugin-version-1-3-released/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-wp-plugin-version-1-3-released/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:39:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"Google News Just Better retirement";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~3/V_-6Sg-RfqI/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"http://stefonthenet.com/google-news-just-better-retirement/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sun, 12 Aug 2012 06:15:50 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"http://stefonthenet.com/?p=1325";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:315:"I have released a new version of my plugin Google News Just Better, the 1.4 purely to inform the users, it wont be maintained any longer. It still perfectly works with the current version of wordpress, the 3.4.1 but all its functionalities are taken over by RSS just better my other plugin. So please, use [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Stef";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:616:"<p>I have released a new version of my plugin <a href="http://stefonthenet.com/google-news-widget-shortcode-plugin/" target="_blank">Google News Just Better</a>, the 1.4 purely to inform the users, it wont be maintained any longer. It still perfectly works with the current version of wordpress, the 3.4.1 but all its functionalities are taken over by <a href="http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-plugin-for-wordpress/" target="_blank">RSS just better</a> my other plugin.<br />\nSo please, use this instead.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.co