";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:355:"Here we go again. Yes, previous version was 0.8. I have skipped two versions. Still no possibility of viewing images/media in this version, however: The date (weekdays &#38; months) is now &#8220;localized&#8221; (=displayed in the language your wordpress is installed) The user is able to display items published only by a given amount of hours [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Stef";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1178:"<p>Here we go again. Yes, previous version was 0.8. I have skipped two versions.</p>\n<p>Still no possibility of viewing images/media in this version, however:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The date (weekdays &amp; months) is now &#8220;localized&#8221; (=displayed in the language your wordpress is installed)</li>\n<li>The user is able to display items published only by a given amount of hours (for infrequently updated feeds)</li>\n<li>The user is able to display Google News feeds given the new params: localization, topic or search keyword(s), local (for Us &amp; Ca news only)</li>\n<li>The preview of the excerpt on mouse-over is disabled if the excerpt is ticked-off (widget)/set to TRUE (shortcode)</li>\n<li>Documentation and explanations have been improved</li>\n<li>Error messages are now better detailed</li>\n<li>Fixed path to RSS image from &#8216;../RSS-just-better/..&#8217; to &#8216;../rss-just-better/..&#8217; (thanks Mike)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>As a matter of fact, this plugin now can fully replace my other plugin Google News just better. I am checking how to retire it elegantly.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~4/1P2Fz6WvX5E" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:66:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-version-1-1-released/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-version-1-1-released/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:39:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43:"RSS Just Better Plugin version 0.8 released";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~3/vzVDIGAbB10/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-plugin-version-0-8-released/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sun, 08 Jul 2012 09:46:35 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"http://stefonthenet.com/?p=1257";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:334:"This version includes a few new features: Being able to truncate/limit the title to (given) chars Being able to choose the date and the time format Being able to sort the feed items by title (instead of the default date/time) Some changes and bug fixes: &#8220;Link to author&#8221; in widget form becomes &#8220;Link to the [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Stef";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1476:"<p>This version includes a few new features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Being able to truncate/limit the title to (given) chars</li>\n<li>Being able to choose the date and the time format</li>\n<li>Being able to sort the feed items by title (instead of the default date/time)</li>\n</ul>\n<div>Some changes and bug fixes:</div>\n<ul>\n<li>&#8220;Link to author&#8221; in widget form becomes &#8220;Link to the Plugin Homepage&#8221;</li>\n<li>The popup window showing on mouseover title is limited to 400 char</li>\n<li>Optimized function to retrieve feed and format list</li>\n<li>Changed error message when feed URL does not return the items list:  if it has already worked before, it must be just a feed temporary issue and not a misformatted feed</li>\n<li>Fixed the plugin homepage URI in the readme.txt file</li>\n</ul>\n<div>Pages on <a href="http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-plugin-for-wordpress/rss-just-better-usage-sample/">how to use it</a> and better <a href="http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-plugin-for-wordpress/demo-rss-just-better-plugin/">demo</a> have also been added to this blog.</div>\n<p>Now,  for the users who wait for the ability to read and display images within the feed, please be patient it&#8217; s a major change and I&#8217;m still working/thinking about it.</p>\n<p>Any comment or remark please drop me a live via the contact form.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~4/vzVDIGAbB10" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-plugin-version-0-8-released/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-plugin-version-0-8-released/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:39:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43:"RSS Just Better Plugin version 0.7 released";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~3/05EC5unpTto/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-plugin-version-0-7-released/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 22 Mar 2012 19:23:05 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"http://stefonthenet.com/?p=1190";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:327:"A bunch of bug fixes mainly notified by kind &#038; patient users of this plugin. Main changes are: Bug Fix: The [&#8230;] in the excerpt linked to the description and not to the URL of the linked item/article [Thx ] Bug Fix: &#8220;Num. of News&#8221; in widget form becomes &#8220;No. of Items&#8221; Bug Fix: Fixed [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Stef";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:847:"<p>A bunch of bug fixes mainly notified by kind &#038; patient users of this plugin.</p>\n<p>Main changes are: </p>\n<ul>\n<li> Bug Fix: The [&#8230;] in the excerpt linked to the description and not to the URL of the linked item/article [Thx ]\n<li> Bug Fix: &#8220;Num. of News&#8221; in widget form becomes &#8220;No. of Items&#8221;\n<li> Bug Fix: Fixed the shortcode example in readme.txt as contained syntax errors [Thx Wayne]\n<li> Bug Fix: The strings for titles and excerpts were not properly formatted for display on screen [Thx Mary Ann]\n<li> Change: Improved documentation for page Other Notes\n</ul>\n<p>Please, read the <a href="http://stefonthenet.com/rss-just-better-plugin-for-wordpress/">plugin homepage</a> for the complete update.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~4/05EC5unpTto" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"